6ff94b9c61bg-053.jpg?height=427&width=401&top__y=980&top__x=468","line":1060,"embedded":true},{"title":"|764x188","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-055.jpg?height=256&width=1043&top__y=1369&top__x=362","line":1091,"embedded":true},{"title":"0, \\frac{\\sqrt{5}}{5}\\.$ )；\r\n(4) $\\triangle F M N$ 周长的最小值为 $\\sqrt{2}+1$.\r\n\r\n其中正确结论的为（）\r\nA. (1)(2)\r\nB. (2)(3)\r\nC. (3)(4)\r\nD. (1)(4)\r\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-078.jpg?height=427&width=404&top__y=980&top__x=466","line":1534},{"title":"2,+\\infty)$\r\nD. $(-\\infty, 2) \\cup(2,+\\infty)$\r\n\r\n#### 10.2.2 【 练 1-1\r\n\r\n圆 $x^{2}+y^{2}+4 \\sin \\theta \\cdot x+4 \\cos \\theta \\cdot y+1=0$ 的半径等于 $\\qquad$ .\r\n\r\n#### 10.2.3 【 练 1-2\r\n\r\n已知 $A(-2,2) ， B(2,6)$ ，则以 $A B$ 为直径的圆的标准方程为 $\\qquad$ .\r\n\r\n#### 10.2.4 【 练 1-3\r\n\r\n正方形草地 $A B C D$ 边长 $1.2 ， E$ 到 $A B ， A D$ 距离为 $0.2 ， F$ 到 $B C ， C D$ 距离为 0.4 ，有个圆形通道经过 $E ， F$ ，且与 $A D$ 只有一个交点，求圆形通道的周长 $\\qquad$ . (精确到 $0.01)$\r\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-118.jpg?height=318&width=304&top__y=889&top__x=299","line":2226},{"title":"                                                             | 201x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=201&top__y=1293&top__x=738","line":2683,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 212x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=212&top__y=1513&top__x=723","line":2684,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 201x156","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=156&width=201&top__y=1742&top__x=738","line":2685,"embedded":true},{"title":"|401x429","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-161.j